ActOther Than Statutory Authority
SubjectProtocol Amending the Avoidance of Double Taxation and the Prevention of Fiscal Evasion with respect to Taxes on Income and on Capital French Republic
PrecisOrder authorizing the Minister of Foreign Affairs to ratify, on behalf of the Government of Canada, the Protocol Amending the Convention between the Government of Canada and the Government of the French Republic for the AVOIDANCE OF DOUBLE TAXATION AND THE PREVENTION OF FISCAL EVASION WITH RESPECT TO TAXES ON INCOME AND ON CAPITAL signed on 2 May 1975, as amended by the Protocol signed on January 16, 1987 and as further amended by the Protocol signed November 30, 1995.
